data.description: This 4 bed, 3 bath, single level home with over 2300 square feet offers an abundance of space for all your needs. Open-concept layout with plank flooring throughout. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary dream: stainless-steel appliances, quartz counters, a gas range, a spacious pantry, and an eat-in kitchen island.  The backyard has a covered patio adorned with string lights, artificial grass, and stylish pavers; a perfect space for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. The master suite with a private bath and separate tub and shower is secluded from the main living area. Why wait to pay more for a new build? Make this dream house your own today.
